title: Will Bobby Be The Next Bachelor? + Lunchbox & Eddie Call Bobby Out On His Mirror Ball Tattoo
itunes:title: Will Bobby Be The Next Bachelor? + Lunchbox & Eddie Call Bobby Out On His Mirror Ball Tattoo
description:
Bobby addresses an article that came out saying he is a front runner to be the next Bachelor on ABC. Lunchbox and Eddie call Bobby out for “copping out” on his mirror ball tattoo. Also, the show talks about if they’d try a new “Urine Therapy” health trend.
